show.description: When elderly parents travel to surprise their son in the city, they uncover a world of lies, betrayal, and buried truths. Man from the hills is an emotional rollercoaster that explores love, pride, and the dark cost of ambition. How far can a son go to erase his roots?  Watch Now !
